channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: What Is Harris Hiding? Peter Doocy Busts Kamala for Ditching the Press Pool
Police ally of scandal-ridden Mayor Tiffany Henyard indicted on bankruptcy fraud charges
item.description: A top police officer and supporter of scandal-plagued Dolton, Illinois, Mayor Tiffany Henyard has been indicted by a federal grand jury in Chicago on bankruptcy fraud charges.

item.title: Ukraine Pounds Russia With Drones, Advancing Deeper
item.description: Ukraine pounded Russian regions with missiles and drones on Wednesday as Kyiv said it was advancing deeper in the biggest foreign incursion into Russia for decades, which the White House said posed a "real dilemma" for President Vladimir Putin.

item.title: Rep. Ilhan Omar Wins Democratic Primary in MN-05
'Rubber-stamped': Key Dem hit over Biden-Harris support on border, inflation
item.description: Sen. Jacky Rosen is being targeted by the NRSC for her support of the Biden-Harris administration and their agenda.

item.title: Rep. Ilhan Omar Wins Minnesota Primary, Opponent Laments Money Won
item.description: Rep. Ilhan Omar, R-Minn., one of the progressive House members known as the "Squad" and a sharp critic of how Israel has conducted the war in Gaza, has won her primary race in Minnesota.

Trump push to dismantle Education Department met with enthusiasm in House GOP
item.description: Rep. Thomas Massie told Fox News Digital about his push to dismantle the Department of Education after it was a policy platform echoed by Trump.

item.title: CNN Analyst Enten: Don't Celebrate Harris Victory Just Yet
item.description: A CNN polling analyst is warning Democrats not to pop the champagne just yet over a Kamala Harris election victory.

item.title: Celery Has to Be Good for Something - Maybe, Concealing Meth?
Former Minnesota resident unloads on Gov Walz after mother died 'of loneliness' during pandemic
item.description: A former Minnesota resident told Fox News Digital she moved out of the state due to Gov. Tim Walz's policies on coronavirus and rampant crime

item.title: NY Times: Hunter Biden Sought State Dept. Help for Burisma
item.description: Hunter Biden solicited help from the State Department in 2016 to land an energy project in Italy while his father, Joe Biden, was the sitting vice president in the Obama administration, the New York Times reported Tuesday night.

item.title: Biden Randomly Starts Screaming at Cancer Event, Appears to Forget What Year It Is and Obama's Name
Trump campaign picks up the pace, eyes counter-programming during Democrats' convention
item.description: With Vice President Kamala Harris riding a wave heading into the Democratic National Convention, former President Trump and his campaign appear to be stepping up their efforts to blunt her momentum.

item.title: Rep. Donalds to Newsmax: Harris, Media Equal 'Death of Democracy'
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris' reticence to discuss any policy positions and the media covering for her amounts to the death of democracy, Rep. Byron Donalds, R-Fla., told Newsmax on Tuesday.
